Package: bvi
Version: 1.3.2
Revision: 1

Description: Curses based binary file editor
DescDetail: <<
bvi is a display-oriented editor for binary files, based on the vi text
editor. If you are familiar with vi, just start the editor and begin to
edit! If you never heard about vi, maybe bvi is not the best choice for
you.
<<

